So proficiency?

01:01:50.067 --> 01:01:53.267
PATRICK: Uh, so down, like you can soak
up another 30, I'm assuming?

01:01:53.300 --> 01:02:00.100
MARISHA: Yeah, I have 118 max, so.

01:02:00.133 --> 01:02:03.834
PATRICK: Then, yeah,
soak up a full 35.

01:02:03.868 --> 01:02:05.434
TALIESIN: Whoa, there you go.

01:02:05.467 --> 01:02:06.701
Are we calling
this a short rest?

01:02:06.734 --> 01:02:09.400
Is that what's
happening right now?

01:02:09.434 --> 01:02:12.100
Are we having, like, some sort
of spontaneous short rest?

01:02:12.133 --> 01:02:14.057
MATT: If you would like
to take a short rest--

01:02:14.057 --> 01:02:16.400
TALIESIN: Oh, my God.

01:02:16.434 --> 01:02:18.100
LIAM: I got 16 hit dice, man.

01:02:18.133 --> 01:02:21.267
MARISHA: Yeah, I'm gonna burn
a few hit dice as well.

