SAM: Oh, shit, that's true.

01:02:25.467 --> 01:02:27.167
TALIESIN: Yeah, you know,
we just fought two dragons,

01:02:27.200 --> 01:02:29.934
they can handle this.

01:02:29.968 --> 01:02:31.701
MATT: Okay, so you're all
taking a short rest before

01:02:31.734 --> 01:02:33.200
or your going to
the gold and not taking--

01:02:33.234 --> 01:02:35.267
-TRAVIS: Gold.
-MATT: Okay.

01:02:35.300 --> 01:02:36.634
So as you all take a moment--

01:02:36.667 --> 01:02:38.198
TRAVIS: There's a lot
of talking happening,

