So, all the money
here has been amassed

01:04:03.834 --> 01:04:06.734
from the guilds,
from the villagers,

01:04:06.767 --> 01:04:10.100
from the townsfolk,
from the temples,

01:04:10.133 --> 01:04:14.667
from the shops,
from the Cloudtop.

01:04:14.701 --> 01:04:17.734
This is the economy of Emon

01:04:17.767 --> 01:04:20.100
crammed into, at least
a majority of it,

01:04:20.133 --> 01:04:21.868
into a singular cavern.

01:04:21.901 --> 01:04:26.334
TRAVIS: I feel overwhelmed by
the sheer amount of stuff.

