MATT: Well, as based on your
investigation check,

01:04:39.033 --> 01:04:44.734
which is a 15, um, you do
find a couple of fun things.

01:04:44.767 --> 01:04:47.324
You find a...

01:04:48.068 --> 01:04:49.868
TRAVIS: I love it when he
reaches for stuff.

