03:15:13.667 --> 03:15:15.901
your younger years, at least.

03:15:15.934 --> 03:15:23.901
Usually, low level,
employed by various tribal sages

03:15:23.934 --> 03:15:26.567
and wandering,
marauding hordes of orcs

03:15:26.601 --> 03:15:30.267
or knolls that were, you know,
given positions of power

03:15:30.300 --> 03:15:31.767
within their small cultures,

03:15:31.801 --> 03:15:33.167
because they had
begun to harness

03:15:33.200 --> 03:15:35.000
some of the powers
of life and death,

03:15:35.033 --> 03:15:39.501
but nothing that really
left a lasting impression.

03:15:39.534 --> 03:15:43.868
There was one tomb
that you excavated

03:15:43.901 --> 03:15:49.067
that it was beyond
the southern lands

03:15:49.100 --> 03:15:52.434
