and it is where refugees
flee from society.

03:16:13.067 --> 03:16:15.334
It's where folks that want
to live beyond the law

03:16:15.367 --> 03:16:17.767
go and build their own place,

03:16:17.801 --> 03:16:20.534
but south of that
into the jungle,

